  <preparation>Blend sour cream, cilantro and lime juice.  Cover and refrigerate.

Blend chipotles and water at low speed until smooth.  

Combine cabbage salad ingredients.

Season rock cod with salt and pepper, lightly dredge and fry over in 1/2-inch of oil over medium-high heat.  Cook for two minutes, turning once or until cooked through.  Drain onto paper towels.</preparation>
